The paper discusses the stability and robustness of evolutionary algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning and optimization tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and algorithm design, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
